  (7, 'Waramadong', 'adequate', 95, 'There are 2 existing wells supplying the community. Well 1 (old well) supplies the Dormitory while well 2 supplies the residents. Water is supplied on a sectional delivery every other day, since the wells do not have high production to meet the demand of the entire community at once. A battery system was recently installed on the community well which has brought improvement to the level of service. The dormitory well draws away in the dry periods which affects the schools.', 'A new well has been awarded to commence by  end of June 2026 to interconect to the dormitory and village to alleviate water challenges in the dry periods', 'Some residents are living great distances along the river cannot be served from the existing water system. Tanks, zinc sheets to be provided for rainwater harvesting. FUNDING NEEDED', NULL, 'School has independent well system that provides water to the Dorms and Secondary school. Village water system provides water for the Nursery and primary school. School well draws away during dry season, as such a new well is being drilled by GWI'),
  (7, 'Kaikan', 'adequate', 95, 'Existing system includes drilled well, wooden trestle, PV and pipe network supplying community. A battery system was recently installed on the community well which has brought improvement to the level of service. There are some new houses beyond the end of the pipe network which will require extension works to provide water to them.', 'Extension of pipe network for new households to be done in 2026. Feasilbitiy being done for small iron removal plant installation improve water quality since the well has very high iron content', 'Some residents are living great distances along the river cannot be served from the existing water system. Tanks, zinc sheets to be provided for rainwater harvesting. FUNDING NEEDED', NULL, 'School connected to main water system and is receiving adequate access. Water has high iron content, as such GWI is looking at small iron removal plant installation for 2026. FUNDING NEEDED'),
